flowchart TD
    A[Analysis specification<br/>analysis/Higgs-to-diphoton.json] --> B[Summary normalization<br/>analysis/config/load_summary.py]
    B --> C[Runtime and preflight<br/>analysis/preflight.py]
    C --> D[Sample registry and semantics<br/>analysis/samples/registry.py]
    D --> E[Nominal signal choice<br/>generator and decay preference]
    D --> F[Nominal prompt-diphoton template choice<br/>smallest mass window covering 105-160 GeV]
    E --> G[Event processing<br/>analysis/hists/histmaker.py]
    F --> G
    G --> H[Object selection<br/>photons and jets]
    H --> I[Exclusive category assignment<br/>analysis/selections/engine.py]
    I --> J[Event payloads and mass templates]
    J --> K[Background candidate scan on observed sidebands]
    J --> L[Prompt-diphoton template scaling and smoothing check]
    L --> M[Spurious-signal tests]
    K --> N[Background-PDF choice per category]
    M --> N
    J --> O[Signal PDF fit from nominal Higgs MC]
    N --> P[Combined category likelihood]
    O --> P
    P --> Q[Central fit]
    Q --> R[Blinded path<br/>expected-only measurement dataset]
    Q --> S[Unblinded path<br/>observed measurement dataset]
    P --> T[Expected significance<br/>exact S+B Asimov RooDataHist]
    P --> U[Observed significance<br/>observed per-category datasets]
    R --> V[Artifacts and plots]
    S --> V
    T --> V
    U --> V
    V --> W[Reviewers, gates, and final handoff]
    X[Skill contracts under .codex/skills] --> C
    X --> D
    X --> N
    X --> T
    X --> W
